  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aspirin is very common in older patients. Therefore many of the investigators patients have
      aspirin. The aim of the study is to proof that Transurethral Surgery of the bladder or the
      prostate can be performed with aspirin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
